n=E2=80=99s contributions to information theory broadly extend far beyond w=
hat Dixon laid out above =E2=80=94 but it also feels misplaced: while techn=
ically speaking everything an AI assistant is doing is ultimately composed =
of 1s and 0s, the manner in which they operate is emergent from their train=
